balance sheets, was $8.6 billion and $7.9 billion at
December 31, 2019 and 2018, respectively. The amount of
commitments related to these investments, which are reported
in accounts payable and other liabilities on the Firm’s
Consolidated balance sheets, was $2.8 billion and $2.3 billion
at December 31, 2019 and 2018, respectively.
